data.description: Welcome Home! This inviting 2-bedroom, 1-bath home is MOVE-IN READY! It's the perfect place for you, whether it's your ideal starter or forever home. The large den could effortlessly be transformed into a third bedroom or a functional home office, giving you the flexibility, you need for every chapter of your homeownership journey. The large eat-in kitchen offers tons of counter and cabinet space and comes fully equipped with appliances. Enjoy the roomy laundry room with ample storage, making daily tasks a breeze with included washer and dryer. Don't forget the full-access attic space, perfect for storage or creating a delightful playroom for your family. Situated on a spacious 1-acre lot, this property features an inviting above-ground 24ft pool, a generously large deck for entertaining, and a delightful wooden swing set.  You have room for play, gardening, and outdoor entertainment, what more could you need? A 10X18 storage building complete with a new metal roof provides extra storage space for all your needs. The large, attached carport delivers an abundance of covered space for your vehicles and versatility for a multitude of purposes. Rest easy with emergency backup gas wall unit heat, a new metal roof, an upgraded 200-amp electrical service, a new forced gas HVAC unit, new fascia boards and 6in gutters, and a crawl space fitted with a vapor barrier. Conveniently located just minutes from I-64, this home ensures easy access to all your destinations. This property is the definition of comfort and practicality. Don't miss out on this opportunity - schedule a showing today and make this your forever home!
